Nexeon MedSystems, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 11:58 PM ET
Healthcare Equipment and Supplies

Company Overview of Nexeon MedSystems, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Nexeon MedSystems Inc., a bioelectronics company, develops and commercializes medical devices for the treatment of chronic medical conditions. It engages in providing physician-driven medical device for the treatment of cardiovascular disease; and intravascular drug delivery system technology platform. The company is also involved in developing and commercializing an implantable neurostimulation and recording platform. Nexeon MedSystems Inc. was founded in 2015 and is headquartered in Lexington, Kentucky.


