Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Medical Equipment & Devices
Sub-Industry: Medical Devices
Nexeon MedSystems Inc operates as a bioelectronics company. The Company develops active medical devices for the treatment of chronic medical conditions. Nexeon MedSystems focuses on developing traditional device technologies such as electronics, software, mechanical engineering, and material science, as well as pharmaceuticals and protein chemistry.




